title: Alexandria City Manager Jinks on The City of Millenials (Audio)
itunes:title: Alexandria City Manager Jinks on The City of Millenials (Audio)
description:
(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: Mark Jinks, City Manager for Alexandria, VA, on the city’s economy, tourism positioning and plans for development. Broadcasting live from the Kimpton Morrison House Hotel in Alexandria, Virginia.
